{"type":null,"faqId":17661,"title":"荣耀6Plus如何使用 NFC 支付进行消费？","answer":"<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">在荣耀钱包客户端进行空中开卡和充值后，就可以在中国境内有银联标识及“QuickPass”闪付标识的 POS 机刷手机消费。</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">注：招商银行一闪通，在刷手机消费时将自动转联机交易，您在POS 机输入绑定一卡通密码，从一卡通上扣除消费金额。<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"443","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1419562690000,"seriesProductName":"Pine-TL10","visitedTimes":517,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":6,"times":2,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"NFC,支付,消费,荣耀6 Plus","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}